         require(!locked, "No reentrancy");
         locked = true;
         _;
         locked = false;
     }
     ```

2. **Check-Effects-Interactions Pattern:**
   - Ensure that all state changes are made before any external calls. This pattern helps prevent reentrancy by ensuring that the contract's state is updated before any potentially malicious calls are made.
